summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and providing for the rezoning of west 86 feet - 1 inch of the south 10 feet of Lot 11, and the west 86 feet - 1 inch of Lot 12, Block 3, Miller's 2nd Addition, with respect to Use Districts, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, by adding thereto one new section numbered 2-231.
